title: Clover Under My Feet
description: May Han is a mutant in a world where people are divided into five species: dogs, cats, rabbits, tigers, and foxes. May, despite being a rabbit, is abnormally tall, and has been bullied her entire life for being such a mutant. What will happen when she meets another mutant, Jun Kang? Will she be able to reconcile her traumatizing past and find love in this unforgiving world?
author: TASSO
